{"tid":1023353,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"1條毒L • 80日 • 中美洲9悠遊","createTime":"2019-02-15T16:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T18:23:03.000Z","uid":10189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f004f228038bd5414466646ce344918cf066c0bf","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"好耐之前出過兩次post<br />\n今次想分享吓好少香港人去既中美洲<br />\n兩年前一個7個月既旅行<br />\n其中80日就喺中美洲玩<br />\n咁點解去中美洲玩<br />\n其實係南美同北美都去過<br />\n純粹集郵填吓窿<br />\n同埋想襯古巴未被3G網絡化之前<br />\n去感受返無得碌手提電話既時光<br />\n<br />\n當時一直由西岸玩落去<br />\n由加州San Diego開始<br />\n一直玩到落巴拿馬城<br />\n簽證當然係最19既<br />\n中間都發生過好撚煩既經歷<br />\n另外治安呢方面就自己醒水<br />\n我都見過有鬼佬坐巴士求其擺野比人粒走個袋<br />\n不過我自己後期去到上Chicken bus可以即刻訓教既境界<br />\n<br />\n如果比較南美<br />\n中美景點無咁出名<br />\n旅遊開發都無咁高<br />\n不過識講英文既人既比例比較高<br />\n始終都係美帝既後花園<br />\n墨西哥雖然聽落去好似好危險<br />\n但d人真係好到仆街<br />\n而且你可以好感受到佢地好積極happy生活態度<br />\n上海好似有直航去墨西哥城<br />\n其實都幾推薦去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieafJn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FieafJn4.png&h=0e5c4926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係今次去咗玩既地圖<br />\n有D走馬看花有D9 hea<br />\n不過之前梁彦宗玩50日都拍到旅遊特輯<br />\n咁毒L玩多30日用黎9heahea都唔算好過份<br />\n鑑於上兩次爭d難尾既經歷<br />\n今次應該會勤力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ba61fce076bb392d27ab5424c121b15a2124ee","tid":1023353,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51a851e3186cba498c0625b378bcce4fb5fdaa9","tid":1023353,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"識唔識Spanish"},{"pid":"fd75939a32a1e4b7ecd3ee095851f6b3a8868d82","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"留名支持下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba3a493ff7c1ea99000c42b6b34bf816243cc3c","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c51a851e3186cba498c0625b378bcce4fb5fdaa9","tid":1023353,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"識唔識Spanish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔識呀<br />\n其實識數字同d基本野就得"},{"pid":"796ade08781b6681fcf6e691aade4645d65b4b92","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"喺美帝hea左差唔多一個月<br />\n終於要向中美洲出發<br />\n墨西哥喺地理版塊上算北美<br />\n不過都係西語國家咁通常旅行都當中美洲<br />\nSan Diego係美墨兩國其中一個重要既邊境點<br />\nHostel都有d墨西哥人放幾日假就過黎玩<br />\n不過佢地都要簽證<br />\n而且都幾難度高<br />\nSan Diego市中心坐50分鐘輕鐵就會到邊境San Ysidro<br />\n墨西哥嗰邊係Tijuana<br />\n美帝出境係無人理<br />\n所以通常落墨西哥好快<br />\n但返上去就好煩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYnJ59L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYnJ59L.png&h=abe03504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSan Diego輕鐵<br />\n得幾條線<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n我個美簽係做咗落本BNO度<br />\n同9成9港燦美簽喺特衰唔同<br />\n其實係方便好撚多<br />\n不過呢個issue就好後話<br />\n<br />\n去到San Ysidro其實車站有個牌指示出境<br />\n不過我係要去機場<br />\n所以我就去左隔離個汽車站<br />\n嗰度有shuttle送你去一個好特別既border point<br />\n呢個就係直接去Tijuana機場<br />\n情況有d似澳門人坐船直接去香港機場<br />\n墨西哥個機場係起到貼住個邊境<br />\n咁坐內陸機就一定平過國際線<br />\nshuttle會送你去美帝嗰邊既邊境<br />\n然後出示passport機票比地勤<br />\n佢確認你係免簽證無問題<br />\n就會叫行入去免税店<br />\n行到尾就有immigration<br />\nBNO一望到三秒就stamp<br />\n之後就會直接到侯機大堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GB4DU3n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGB4DU3n.png&h=2dd8a193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSan Ysidro既出境指示牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axK4QBW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxK4QBW.png&h=f9156a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由美帝行過去墨西哥<br />\n呢排邊境圍牆好heat<br />\n其實之前由鳳凰城坐灰狗巴去San Diego<br />\n成條邊境好多位都起左呢d欄<br />\n我記得中間停過一個Mexicali既地方係睇得超清楚"},{"pid":"c28c7a0211e8bf2e7f55456046286da1f5be0f4a","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"繼續支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打去古巴係Havana Trinidad 同 Santiago de Cuba？<br />\n中美只去過Belize 同 Guatemala，兩邊既人都相當友善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbda6b1c3ee25adb5a24f2d7290dd3a18ebd4b84","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c28c7a0211e8bf2e7f55456046286da1f5be0f4a","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"繼續支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打去古巴係Havana Trinidad 同 Santiago de Cuba？<br />\n中美只去過Belize 同 Guatemala，兩邊既人都相當友善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打幾個post都有支持<br />\n係呀得10日唔可以玩咁多<br />\n同埋我去嗰陣係7月尾到10月頭<br />\n係最撚熱最撚大雨<br />\n好多時都出唔到去玩<br />\n試過之後洪水國家進入緊急狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f20c10b94fb0899620f58f2f0f77c11616e3d8e","tid":1023353,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155deced1365395db78651a543ef168e55c5618f","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"之前喺San Yisdro都換左d錢<br />\n去到機場都係無所事事<br />\n墨西哥有好多廉航<br />\n我今次就揀左Interjet飛去墨西哥城(CDMX)<br />\nInterjet都係價錢吸引同埋風評唔錯<br />\n墨西哥北部就唔多旅遊資源<br />\n得大城市Monterray<br />\n所以決定一野就決定飛去CDMX<br />\n<br />\n機程三個半鐘<br />\n廉航但係有杯野飲同埋有包零食，都幾佛心<br />\n墨西哥其實都幾撚大吓<br />\n之後坐巴士好多都幾長途<br />\n去到墨西哥城機場出機係完全無指示<br />\n真係走咗好撚耐先知邊到攞行李<br />\n攞完行李最重要係攞錢<br />\n因為出發前柒咗唔記得咗搞張visa既提款卡<br />\n所以成個中美洲旅行都係比呢個issue<br />\n試左幾家銀行，得一間肯嘔錢比銀聯<br />\n<br />\n出機場之前最重要係整返張交通卡<br />\n要搵一部機仔去買卡再入credit先上到機場巴<br />\n機場有個tourist information booth仔但d人好撚廢<br />\n最後搞左一大輪先搞到<br />\n出機場可以搭機場巴或者地鐵<br />\n不過我出境嗰個時間已經放工時間<br />\n費時咩住個backpack又可能比人爬野就緊係搭巴士<br />\n我去嗰陣港紙兑墨西哥披索係1:2.1(而家1:2.4)<br />\n程巴士30披即係14蚊左右<br />\n墨西哥物價係好9平(尤其啱啱去完美帝)<br />\n<br />\n架機場巴都幾撚on9<br />\n兜黎兜去仲要又好撚塞車<br />\n直線距離7公里行撚左兩個鐘<br />\n儍的嗎<br />\n<br />\n搵左間hostel係Hidalgo地鐵站<br />\n狀況麻麻不過位置幾好<br />\n第一日都浪費係交通<br />\n都做唔到d咩"},{"pid":"c1574ce83b66a3614818f552656dbb3445576bd2","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:23:59.000Z","msg":"屌忙咗成個月<br />\n唔可以起左個頭就無左回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥城比人感覺就係治安會唔會唔好<br />\n市中心嘅Tepito Market更加出晒名差<br />\n嗰度入口附近都會有d女人街feel既野賣<br />\n但愈行愈入就會有槍、稀有動物賣<br />\n由於怕死怕比人老笠<br />\n最後都係決定唔去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLw8SeO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLw8SeO.png&h=12491989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅館附近既Plaza de la Republica<br />\n去到大城市都係感受下個城市既節奏<br />\n通常都唔會安排衝景點<br />\n反而周圍行認識下個城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zUOWgH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUOWgH2.png&h=86355b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行幾步就係Alaneda Central Park<br />\n如果講市中心個氣氛同埋感覺<br />\n墨西哥城真係幾舒服<br />\n唔會有南美嗰堆大城市怕突然比人搶野<br />\n好乾淨好企理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27QJGaX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27QJGaX.png&h=3a15e1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔兩三條街既唐人街<br />\n好細、無乜華人<br />\n我諗既然留得墨西哥<br />\n可能一早都索性北上去咗美帝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2vYu4W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2vYu4W.png&h=1b0b3596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥城地標之一，Palacio de Bella Artes<br />\n就喺正個公園隔離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70xsoqA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70xsoqA.png&h=86c4367d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7gMDYW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7gMDYW.png&h=5e16c2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥城個舊城中心好大<br />\n有好多博物館、政府機構、教堂<br />\n花一日行呢度都唔夠<br />\n不過有好多都排好多人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VD9qUyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVD9qUyy.png&h=8cd0f44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後成日都喺呢個舊城中心行<br />\n乜9都無做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqDWgNP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqDWgNP.png&h=98f6f029&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXvEY1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXvEY1a.png&h=5543603c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無做過野但喺墨西哥城<br />\n一定要做嘅就係掃街<br />\n市中心有超級多街邊檔<br />\n全部都係蔗渣既價錢<br />\n燒鵝既味道<br />\n<br />\n呢個係Tartas<br />\n類似三文治<br />\n一個30-40pesos左右<br />\n圍返都唔洗廿蚊港紙<br />\n入面通常係一款肉加醬<br />\n一個已經好撚飽<br />\n基本上都唔洗再食到其他野<br />\n所以通常我都係早餐先會食"},{"pid":"2c0192addbe2073bd5153d8111fc05219efbb61b","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"巴打墨西哥都未完就爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8580a7ae8d160025be3bb2e715dbf732eff422f5","tid":1023353,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c0192addbe2073bd5153d8111fc05219efbb61b","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"巴打墨西哥都未完就爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"見到新開既POST 加上中美洲 即刻bookmark左先遲D睇<br />\n結果..."},{"pid":"608580dcb1ee901880fe276e358b6c31c6b0a8f5","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以比佢爛尾<br />\n我慢慢打都死哂個遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中美洲對於香港人黎講<br />\n分分鐘仲冷門過去東非南非<br />\n因為時間上去到咁遠倒不如去南美洲<br />\n去東南非既話嗰度d人好多都係英聯邦國家<br />\n識講英文點都方便d<br />\n再加上中美國家簽證煩治安又差<br />\n我上網都搵唔到幾多update既香港人遊記<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥其實係多個中美洲文明既發源地<br />\n最出名當然係尤卡坦半島附近既瑪雅文明<br />\n不過瑪雅係時間軸黎講算係比較近代<br />\n中間都有幾個前哥倫布時代既文明<br />\n墨西哥城最出名既景點<br />\n就係離市中心東北四十公里左右既Teotihuacan<br />\n中文通常叫佢做日月金字塔<br />\n佢係大概公元元年前後發展既一個文明<br />\n最巔峰係有成廿萬人住<br />\n基本上去得墨西哥城都一定要花半日時間過去<br />\n<br />\n去日月金字塔要搭地鐵去巴士北站<br />\n雖然墨西哥城出名治安差<br />\n不過我覺得搭地鐵又唔係想像中咁差<br />\n係轉線有陣時真係要行好耐<br />\n巴士北站係超級大既一個汽車站<br />\n有間巴士公司係會好密咁樣開車過去<br />\n見最多遊客look既counter就係<br />\n坐個零鐘就會到日月金字塔<br />\n巴士會係景區門口放低你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lr03CcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLr03CcD.png&h=81d2c519&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLmZaxE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLmZaxE.png&h=453b571d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日月金字塔係一個超級大既景點<br />\n如果龜速行加影相都要幾個鐘<br />\n一入到景點區最近係太陽金字塔<br />\n比較高嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7CtOj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7CtOj5.png&h=17f5d253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPOXGE6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPOXGE6.png&h=1eb04a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太陽金字塔<br />\n呢兩座金字塔都係可以比你行上去<br />\n而且斜度唔算太高<br />\n最頂嗰個平台都容納到幾多人<br />\n只係人流都幾撚多<br />\n要行上去都係要等吓前面d肥人慢慢行上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxg6z0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxg6z0Q.png&h=6cdbec04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由太陽金字塔塔頂望出去<br />\n對面嗰座就係月亮金字塔<br />\n連接住兩個塔中間嗰條路叫亡者之路<br />\n大概三百米長左右<br />\n沿途會有好多細既complex可以爬上去<br />\n可以用唔同既角度欣賞兩座塔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbfnSOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbfnSOu.png&h=c2ba4ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DGFEtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DGFEtw.png&h=732d2645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉個頭就鼠咗上月亮金字塔<br />\n呢座塔條樓梯比較斜<br />\n畏高就靠中間有d扶手比你<br />\n我自己覺得月亮金字塔個景靚d<br />\n可以望到晒成條亡者之路<br />\n<br />\n最後我都喺呢度hea咗三個半鐘<br />\n唔算長唔算短喇<br />\n成個景區仲有d次景點<br />\n仲有博物館<br />\n真係行撚死人<br />\n<br />\n出口附近有巴士返墨西哥城<br />\n我自己就無搭到去總站<br />\n係市區北面就落左車<br />\n因為搭車見到有座教堂好遠睇過去都幾得意<br />\n所以就早左落車"},{"pid":"a5e02e8a0843aaa04b5c833b19d4546b62889690","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"無喇喇落車都係因為見到有座圓環型既座堂超得意<br />\n嗰度係叫Basilica de our lady of Guadalupe<br />\n係一座新同舊既教堂組成既一個大廣場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4y8OrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4y8OrL.png&h=c89afe5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O8wMdr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O8wMdr.png&h=c5859045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圓型嗰個係新嘅<br />\n兩個其實係隔離<br />\n圓型嗰個入面keep住有d聖經講<br />\n當然前提係你要係教徒又識西班牙文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vqwye7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqwye7f.png&h=2e2f56f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXYMz7h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXYMz7h.png&h=489aa476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大廣場隔離有個公園仔<br />\n可以跟住d人行上去<br />\n睇晒成個廣場既setting<br />\n嗰度好多一家大細既local去過日晨<br />\n治安感覺良好<br />\n都幾值得路過停一停去吓<br />\n<br />\n玩咗大半日都係醫肚<br />\n墨西哥野食比人感覺係辣<br />\n其實係錯覺黎<br />\n辣只係你自己後加上去<br />\n本身d野食一d都唔辣<br />\n同埋好撚好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjBirfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjBirfc.png&h=adf51223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺墨西哥城周圍都有呢d凍飲<br />\n味道乜9都有<br />\n呢杯椰奶係大杯都係15pesos<br />\n真係飲撚肥人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKUcvHk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKUcvHk.png&h=9a1b3158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n掃街係墨西哥城既生活<br />\n餐廳都係平<br />\n但掃街既機會只有喺嗰度先有<br />\n市區有勁撚多呢d咁既檔仔<br />\n乜9都有<br />\n而且佢地仲明碼實價講好咩野係幾錢<br />\n唔會收貴你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bPWXn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bPWXn0.png&h=476aefe0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krTkEBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrTkEBm.png&h=beffe3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係街邊食Tacos食到飽死<br />\n都唔好話去過墨西哥<br />\n食Tacos就一定要去街邊檔食<br />\n因為佢地係會先燒一燒塊皮<br />\n等佢好咬口d<br />\n然後再放肉同配菜<br />\n價錢其實大同小異<br />\n有d 30pesos5件<br />\n咁嗰5件就比較細件d<br />\n有d就13pesos一件就一件大件d<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmygXo0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmygXo0.png&h=fee7d9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢件Quesadilla同美國食開嗰d唔同<br />\n咁撚大舊都係廿零pesos<br />\n真係食肥人㗎墨西哥<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得就係食粟米<br />\n墨西哥人真係好撚中意食<br />\n佢地會將粟米加芝士粉食<br />\n不過食咁多Tacos都好撚飽<br />\n遲吓再介紹"},{"pid":"c2fab2a3ecf0f2a20d85bdad22fa998ab981a9a1","tid":1023353,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"終於上水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有唔少人睇緊架其實，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f970d2248f572e687e8c4eebc1b4cb3d278cbe88","tid":1023353,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:23:03.000Z","msg":"飲飽食醉就去返市中心周圍行<br />\n夜晚既墨西哥城係非常多人<br />\n去過南美洲或者西班牙既都知佢地中意好夜先食晚飯<br />\n所以條街到夜晚十點都仲好多人<br />\n而且治安感覺良好<br />\n我諗如果你去過南美洲嗰堆首都<br />\n再對比返墨西哥城<br />\n咁墨西哥城真係舒服好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32eDucg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32eDucg.png&h=e171aea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚既美術館<br />\n都係好多人喺度hea<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjWZdEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjWZdEi.png&h=206324cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚九點幾既Zocalo其中一條大街<br />\n超級多人<br />\n最緊要都係提防扒手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2nEX6J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2nEX6J.png&h=c567ea28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DTHVTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DTHVTq.png&h=4fd562f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度有樣好頂癮既街頭表演<br />\n有個actress係會喺露台唱歌<br />\n然後觀眾就係下面睇<br />\n我唔知係自娛定係下面有人收集打賞<br />\n不過呢個型式我真係只有呢度見過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgR6C7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgR6C7q.png&h=82153324&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bybKpNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbybKpNr.png&h=479d26f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥城主座堂<br />\n我去緊嗰陣大廣場大維修<br />\n所以影唔到呢個座堂對出喺一個超巨大既廣場<br />\n真係有d可惜<br />\n<br />\n夜晚既墨西哥城市中心治安黎講<br />\n以中南美洲既標準黎講算係唔錯<br />\n不過到左夜晚好多便利店都會拉閘運作<br />\n所以要入貨一係就早d<br />\n一係就要識西班牙文<br />\n不過就肯定貴過平時買好多"}]}